name: A Child's Imagination
description: A composition of select sketches created in my childhood (2002-2003, age ~10), the legacy of a time spent absolutely in love with drawing. Now, it is a tribute to the rich imagination of a young mind, and the hidden potential within each one of us. A collage of high-quality scans available exclusively on hic et nunc.  Artist: Tushar Chhabra, @tusharshangout
